(51, 1, '2019-05-20 06:39:30', '2019-05-20 06:39:30', '<!-- wp:flatsome/uxbuilder -->\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"3\" span__sm=\"12\" align=\"center\" visibility=\"hide-for-small\"]\n\n[message_box bg_color=\"rgb(255, 212, 0)\" padding=\"0\"]\n\n[row_inner style=\"collapse\" v_align=\"middle\" h_align=\"center\"]\n\n[col_inner span=\"9\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>DANH MC SN PHM</strong></p>\n\n[/col_inner]\n\n[/row_inner]\n\n[/message_box]\n[ux_sidebar id=\"menu-left\"]\n\n[message_box bg_color=\"rgb(255, 212, 0)\" padding=\"0\"]\n\n[row_inner style=\"collapse\" v_align=\"middle\" h_align=\"center\"]\n\n[col_inner span=\"9\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>SN PHM BN CHY</strong></p>\n\n[/col_inner]\n\n[/row_inner]\n\n[/message_box]\n[ux_products_list products=\"4\" orderby=\"sales\" show=\"onsale\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"9\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<div data-html-id=\"959\">\n<h1><strong>QUY CH HOT NG WEBSITE CUNG CP DCH V TMT</strong></h1>\n<p>*p dng t: 1/1/2017</p>\n<h2><strong>I. Nguyn tc chung</strong></h2>\n<p>- Website thng mi in t didongdanang.com do cng ty C Phn Di ng Thng Minh (Cng ty) thc hin hot ng v vn hnh. i tng phc v l tt c khch hng trn 63 tnh thnh Vit Nam c nhu cu mua hng nhng khng c thi gian n siu th hoc t trc  khi n siu th l m bo c hng.</p>\n<p>- Sn phm c kinh doanh ti www.didongdanang.com phi p ng y  cc quy nh ca php lut, khng bn hng nhi, hng khng r ngun gc, hng xch tay.</p>\n<p>- Hot ng mua bn ti didongdanang.com phi c thc hin cng khai, minh bch, m bo quyn li ca ngi tiu dng.</p>\n<h2><strong>II. Quy nh chung</strong></h2>\n<p><u><strong>Tn Min website Thng mi in t:</strong></u></p>\n<p>Website thng mi in t didongdanang.com do Cng ty C phn Th Gii Di ng pht trin vi tn min giao dch l: www.didongdanang.com (sau y gi tt l: Website TMT didongdanang.com)</p>\n<p><u><strong>nh ngha chung:</strong></u></p>\n<p><strong>Ngi bn</strong> l cng ty c phn Di ng Thng Minh.</p>\n<p><strong>Ngi mua</strong>l c