(93, 1, '2019-05-20 07:11:32', '2019-05-20 07:11:32', '<div style=\"height: 400px; white-space: pre-wrap; overflow: auto;\">\r\n<h3><strong><a title=\"Tham kho gi in thoi smartphone Vivo chnh hng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-vivo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Vivo</a>va mang mt chin binh mi n phn khc tm trung gi r c tn<a title=\"Tham kho gi in thoi Vivo Y15s (2021) chnh hng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/vivo-y15s-2021\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Vivo Y15s</a>, mt sn phm s hu kh nhiu u im nh thit k p, mn hnh ln, camera kp, pin cc tru v cn rt nhiu iu th v khc ang ch n bn.</strong></h3>\r\n<h3><strong>Ngoi hnh sang trng, n tng</strong></h3>\r\nVivo Y15s s hu nhiu im tng ng vi nhng \"ngi anh em\"<a title=\"Tham kho gi in thoi Vivo Y15 chnh hng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/vivo-y15\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Vivo Y15</a>ca mnh khi ton b thn my lm bng Polymer cao cp, thit k cong cnh 3D v kiu dang mong nhe ch 8.28 mm em li cm gic cm my trong tay kh thoi mi.\r\n\r\nMt lng hon thin vi ha tit k sc m vi hai ty chn mu sc Xanh Bin Su v Trng c kh nng chuyn sng xanh v cng p mt.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-301021-105513.jpg\"><img class=\" ls-is-cached lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Vivo Y15s | Ngoi hnh sang trng n tng\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-301021-105513.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Vivo Y15s | Ngoi hnh sang trng n tng\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-301021-105513.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nin thoi cn c trang b tnh nng bo mt<a title=\"Tham kho gi in thoi smartphone c bo mt cm bin vn tay\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-bao-mat-van-tay\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">m kha vn tay</a> cnh bn, c tch hp hon ho vi nt ngun  v tr v cng thun li gip ngi dng c th m kha cc nhanh ch trong 0.232 giy.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-301021-105457.jpg\"><img class=\" ls-is-cached lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Vivo Y15s | M kha vn tay  cnh vin\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-301021-105457.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Vivo Y15s | M kha vn tay  cnh vin\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-301021-105457.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nMn hnh ca Vivo Y15s c kch thc ln ti 6.51 inch vi thit k trn vin siu mong hai bn giup tng ty l hin thi hinh anh, tao nn trai nghim quan sat chn thc.  sng ca mn hnh s t ng iu chnh theo iu kin mi trng xung quanh v ch  bo v mt gip gim nh sng xanh, bo v th lc ca bn v mang li tri nghim s dng lun c thoi mi nht.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-261221-094658.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Mn hnh Vivo Y15s\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-261221-094658.jpg\" alt=\"Mn hnh Vivo Y15s\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-261221-094658.jpg\" /></a>\r\n<h3><strong>Sng to khng ngng vi b i camera AI</strong></h3>\r\nVivo Y15s c trang b b i camera sau, camera chnh c  phn gii 13 MP khu  f/2.2 h tr chup nh goc rng, ly net t ng va camera phu 2 MP khu  f/2.4 h tr chp nh macro, my h tr chup<a title=\"Tham kho gi in thoi smartphone camera chp hnh xo phng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-camera-xoa-phong\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">xoa phng</a>vi s gip sc ca tr tu nhn to AI, cho bn sng to khng gii hn trong nhip nh.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-301021-110702.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Vivo Y15s | Sng to khng ngng ngh vi b i camera sau\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-301021-110702.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Vivo Y15s | Sng to khng ngng ngh vi b i camera sau\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-301021-110702.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nBn cnh b i camera sau chuyn nghip, camera trc ca Vivo Y15s cng khng h km cnh vi  phn gii ln ti 8 MP, h tr y  cc tnh nng lm p bng tr tu nhn to AI,  bn lun c c nhng tm hnh tuyt vi trong tng chi tit.\r\n\r\nTrong  c th k ti tnh nng b sng selfie t ng iu chnh  thch ng vi nh sng ca mi trng xung quanh v cng ngh Face Beauty s gi  nhng iu chnh trn gng mt c thit k dnh ring cho bn  bn lun c ta sng trong mi khung nh.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-301021-110705.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Vivo Y15s | Tnh nng b sng khi selfie\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-301021-110705.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Vivo Y15s | Tnh nng b sng khi selfie\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-301021-110705.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nNgoi ra, Y15s cn h tr thm tnh nng<a title=\"Tham kho gi in thoi smartphone c bo mt m kho khun mt\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-bao-mat-khuon-mat\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">nhn din khun mt</a>thng minh, bn ch cn nhc in thoi i din vi khun mt l c th m kha d dng.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-301021-105453.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Vivo Y15s | Tnh nng m kha bng khun mt\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-301021-105453.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Vivo Y15s | Tnh nng m kha bng khun mt\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-301021-105453.jpg\" /></a>\r\n<h3><strong>Hiu nng n nh cho cc tc v c bn hng ngy</strong></h3>\r\nin thoi Vivo Y15s c trang b b vi x l MediaTek Helio P35 8 nhn c tc  ln n 2.3 GHz v sn xut trn tin trnh 12 nm cho hiu nng cao ng thi tit kim nng lng mt cch ti u.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-301021-110832.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Vivo Y15s | Hiu nng mt m\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-301021-110832.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Vivo Y15s | Hiu nng mt m\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-301021-110832.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nVivo Y15s s hu<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi c dung lng RAM 3 GB ang bn ti TGD\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-ram-3gb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">3 GB RAM</a>v<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi c b nh trong t 32 GB\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-rom-32gb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">32 GB b nh trong</a>va   ci t v s dng cc ng dng quan trng thng dng, bn c th lu tr hnh nh, video, d liu khc,... trn th nh ngoi, c h tr th nh c dung lng ti a n 1 TB.\r\n\r\nVivo Y15s trang b h iu hnhAndroid 11 phin bn Go edition (cn c th gi tt l Android Go) -l 1 phin bn ti u, kch thc nh v tit kim d liu hn.Android 11 Go edition ci thin thi gian khi ng ng dng ln 20% (so viAndroid 10 Go edition),thm dung lng lu tr h iu hnh ln n 900 MB v ti a 270 MB b nh RAM trng gip bn thao tc a nhim mt m hn.\r\n\r\nLu  thm: Android 11 Go edition cha h tr cc tnh nng bao gm chia i mn hnh/ca s a nhim, hnh trong hnh, multi display, nhiu ngi dng, hnh nn ng.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-261221-114126.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Android 11 Go edition\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-261221-114126.jpg\" alt=\"Android 11 Go edition\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-261221-114126.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nTrn Vivo Y15s cn c thm ch  Multi-Turbo 3.0, thit k dnh ring cho vic chi game nh cao, tp trung vo vic ti u ha v phn b ti nguyn b nh mt cch hp l gip in thoi c th vn hnh mt m, gim git lag trong cc tr chi.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/249720/vivo-y15s-2021-261221-114435.jpg\"><img cl