(158, 1, '2019-05-20 10:35:13', '2019-05-20 10:35:13', '<div style=\"height: 400px; white-space: pre-wrap; overflow: auto;\">\r\n<h3><strong><a title=\"Tham kho cc dng sn phm smartphone, tablet Samsung chnh hng\" href=\"https://thegioididong.com/samsung\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Samsung</a> chnh thc gii thiu chic in thoi<a title=\"Tham kho gi in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G chnh hng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Galaxy A52s 5G</a>n ngi dng, yphin bn nng cp ca<a title=\"Tham kho gi in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52 5GSamsung Galaxy A52 5G chnh hng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/samsung-galaxy-a52-5g\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Galaxy A52 5G</a>ra mt cch y khng lu, vi ngoi hnh khng i nhng c nng cp ng k v thng s cu hnh bn trong.</strong></h3>\r\n<h3><strong>Thit k c trng Galaxy A</strong></h3>\r\nSamsung Galaxy A52s tip tc s dng ngn ng thit k nguyn khi theo phong cch tr trung vi cc tu chn mu sc nh: en, trng, tm v xanh mint.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-3.jpg\"><img class=\" ls-is-cached lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Thit k tha hng t dng flagship cao cp\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-3.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Thit k tha hng t dng flagship cao cp\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-3.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nMy s dng mn hnh nt rui Super AMOLED kch thc 6.5 inch,  phn gii Full HD+ cng thit k trn vin gip m rng ti a khng gian hin th. T  ngi dng c th thoi mi tn hng nhng chng trnh gii tr cc k hp dn.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-2.jpg\"><img class=\" ls-is-cached lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Mn hnh gii tr sc nt\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-2.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Mn hnh gii tr sc nt\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-2.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nMy h tr tn s qut 120 Hz cng tm nn cht lng gip mi tri nghim vut chm trn my c tr nn mt m, gip mi hnh nh, thc phim trn in thoi u c hin th ti tn v v cng sc nt.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-5.jpg\"><img class=\" ls-is-cached lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Tri nghim s dng vt m sc nt\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-5.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Tri nghim s dng vt m sc nt\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-5.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nSamsung A52s 5G c tng cng bo mt vi<a title=\"Tham kho gi in thoi smartphone c bo mt cm bin vn tay\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-bao-mat-van-tay\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">cm bin vn tay</a>c thit k t ngay di mn hnh, gip bn c th m kha in thoi hay ng nhp d dng bng vn tay m khng cn nhp mt khu.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-4.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Cm bin vn tay trong mn hnh\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-4.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Cm bin vn tay trong mn hnh\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-4.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nBn cnh  Galaxy A52s cn s hu h thng m thanh vm vi v tr phn b loa v cng khoa hc gip bn c th thoi mi tri nghim nhng ta game hay l tn hng nhng pht giy gii tr khi xem phim vi cht m cc .\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-11.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | H thng m thanh cht lng vt tri\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-11.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | H thng m thanh cht lng vt tri\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-11.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nNgoi ra, Galaxy A52s cng c chng nhn IP67 v kh nng<a title=\"Tham kho gi in thoi smartphone chng nc chng bi\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-chong-nuoc-bui\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">khng nc, bi</a>, c th sng st   su 1 mt trong 30 pht ngi dng c th thoi mi tri nghim trong mi iu kin thi tit v mi trng khc nhau.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g--6.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Kh nng khng nc bi bn chun IP67\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g--6.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Kh nng khng nc bi bn chun IP67\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g--6.jpg\" /></a>\r\n<h3><strong>Nng tm sc mnh vi chip rng Snapdragon 778G</strong></h3>\r\nim nng cp ng gi nht ca chic Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G l s dng mt b vi x l mi ca nh Qualcomm mang tn Snapdragon 778G, c sn xut trn tin trnh 6 nm cho hiu nng mnh hn khong 25 - 30% so vi ngi tin nhim.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Nng tm sc mnh vi Snapdragon 778G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Nng tm sc mnh vi Snapdragon 778G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nKt hp vi  l<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi c dung lng RAM 8 GB ang bn ti TGD\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-ram-8gb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">RAM 8 GB</a>gip bn thc hin tc v a nhim c tt hn v mt m hn, cng b giao din OneUI mi nhiu tnh nng em n ngi dng tri nghim s dng tt nht.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-1-1.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Khe sim\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Khe sim\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-1-1.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nNgoi ra, my cng c trang b<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi c b nh trong 128 GB ang bn ti TGD\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-rom-128gb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">b nh trong 128 GB</a>khthoi mi  bn lu gi nhng video, hnh nh m khng lo b y b nh.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-10.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Cu hnh mnh m, chin game mt m\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-10.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Cu hnh mnh m, chin game mt m\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-10.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nc bit Galaxy A52s cn c tch hp cng ngh 5G hin i, gip bn lun kt ni vi th gii vi mt tc  siu nhanh.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g--10-1.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Tch hp cng ngh 5G \" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g--10-1.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Tch hp cng ngh 5G \" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g--10-1.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nNgoi ra. A52s 5G cn c tch hp cng ngh bo mt Samsung Knox gip thit b an ton trnh khi virus hay phn mm c hi khi s dng hng ngy.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g--1.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Cng ngh bo mt bng Samsung Knox\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g--1.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Cng ngh bo mt bng Samsung Knox\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g--1.jpg\" /></a>\r\n<h3><strong>B 4 camera cht lng cao</strong></h3>\r\nSamsung Galaxy A52s tip tc s dng b 4 camera sau vi cm bin chnh 64 MP c chng rung quang hc OIS, cm bin<a title=\"Tham kho gi in thoi smartphone camera chp hnh gc rng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-camera-goc-rong\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">gc siu rng</a>12 MP v 2 cm bin 5 MP cho chp chn dung v<a title=\"Tham kho gi in thoi smartphone camera macro\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-camera-macro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">macro</a>k tha t dng sn phm Galaxy S cao cp.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-9.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Cm 4  camera cht lng cao\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-9.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Cm 4  camera cht lng cao\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-9.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nBn cnh thng s n tng l cc cng ngh v cng hin i nh: H tr chng rung quang hc OIS cao cp gip hnh nh lun m bo cht lng, kh nng ly nt chnh xc ngay c khi bn chp trong iu kin thiu sng.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-9-1.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Kh nng nhp nh trong iu kin thiu sng\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-9-1.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Kh nng nhp nh trong iu kin thiu sng\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-9-1.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nc bit hn, bn c th chp mi th tr nn gn hn vi camera macro  mang li tri nghim y th v. Cng vi , bn c th iu chnh  su trng nh mt cch linh hot v nhanh chng gip nhng bc nh chn dung tr nn n tng hn.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-4-1.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | nh chp bng camera sau\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-4-1.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | nh chp bng camera sau\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-4-1.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nCamera trc trn Samsung A52s c  phn gii 32 MP h tr nhiu tnh nng vt tri vi kh nng ng ly nt, ch  HDR, kh nng nhn din khun mt  bn lun ta sng trong mi trng hp.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g--10.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | nh chp selfie bng camera trc\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g--10.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | nh chp selfie bng camera trc\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g--10.jpg\" /></a>\r\n<h3><strong>Thi lng pin n tng cho tri nghim s dng th ga</strong></h3>\r\nVi Samsung Galaxy A52s bn hon ton c th gii tr bt tn c ngy vi pin c dung lng ln ti 4500 mAh. Bn cnh  cng ngh AI thng minh gip tng thi lng s dng mt cch ti u gip bn c thm thi gian  tri nghim.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-7.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Thi lng pin n tng, thoi mi dng th ga\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-7.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | Thi lng pin n tng, thoi mi dng th ga\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-7.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nNgi dng Galaxy A52s 5G cn c trang b cng ngh<a title=\"Tham kho gi in thoi smartphone sc pin nhanh\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-sac-pin-nhanh\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">sc nhanh</a>ti a25 W, gip bn c th nhanh chng s dng li my, cho tri nghim cuc sng thm trn vn, tuy nhin trong hp my ch c tng km cc sc 15 W.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-8.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | H tr sc nhanh 25W\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-8.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G | H tr sc nhanh 25W\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/247507/samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-8.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nC th ni, Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G khng ch c tha hng thit k tinh t v n tng ca phin bn i trc m chng cn c nng cp kh nhiu v trang b v tnh nng. Chc chn y s l chic smartphone mang n cho ngi dng nhng tri nghim th v kh qun.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'in thoi Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G 128GB', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'dien-thoai-samsung-galaxy-a52s-5g-128gb', '', '', '2022-05-30 04:46:53', '2022-05-30 04:46:53', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=158', 0, 'product', '', 1),
