/42/235838/samsung-galaxy-s22-ultra-11-2.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nC th ni Galaxy S22 Ultra 5G chnh l chic my u tin c tch hp bt S Pen hon ho trong mt thn my ca dng Galaxy S. Gi y, bn c th d dng phc tho, ghi ch li nhng  tng v cng nhanh chng vi  tr  c ci thin cho cm gic vit v v cng chn tht.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/235838/samsung-galaxy-s22-ultra-7-2.jpg\"><img class=\" ls-is-cached lazyloaded\" title=\"Galaxy S22 Ultra 5G - Thao tc vit bng bt S Pen\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/235838/samsung-galaxy-s22-ultra-7-2.jpg\" alt=\"Galaxy S22 Ultra 5G - Thao tc vit bng bt S Pen\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/235838/samsung-galaxy-s22-ultra-7-2.jpg\" /></a>\r\n<h3>Cu hnh mnh m vi Snapdragon 8 Gen 1</h3>\r\nHiu nng trn Galaxy S22 Ultra 5G l iu khi bn ci khi my s dng chip Snapdragon 8 Gen 1 v cng mnh m vi tin trnh sn xut 4 nm. Khi my chi game cng ch m ln mt cht  v tr cm camera ch khng hon ton qu nng nh nhng sn phm khc khi dng cng con chip ny.\r\n\r\nMy d dng vt qua c cc ta game Lin Qun, PUBG Mobile, ci t cu hnh ti a th biu  FPS trn Galaxy S22 Ultra 5G vn kh n nh, khng b drop qu nhiu. K c ta game Genshin Impact  mc  ha mc nh th my chi vn mt m,  ha hin th p mt.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/235838/samsung-galaxy-s22-ultra-1-2.jpg\"><img class=\" ls-is-cached lazyloaded\" title=\"Galaxy S22 Ultra 5G - Tri nghim chi game\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/235838/samsung-galaxy-s22-ultra-1-2.jpg\" alt=\"Galaxy S22 Ultra 5G - Tri nghim chi game\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/235838/samsung-galaxy-s22-ultra-1-2.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nCn ni v cc tc v c bn nh lt web, c bo, xem YouTube,... th my hon thnh mt cch d dng, s dng mt m, kh nng a nhim thoi mi vi<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi c RAM 8 GB kinh doanh ti Thegioididong.com\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-ram-8gb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">RAM 8 GB