\n<div><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/235838/samsung-galaxy-s22-ultra-5-2.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Galaxy S22 Ultra 5G - Mn hnh cong trn sang 2 cnh\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/235838/samsung-galaxy-s22-ultra-5-2.jpg\" alt=\"Galaxy S22 Ultra 5G - Mn hnh cong trn sang 2 cnh\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/235838/samsung-galaxy-s22-ultra-5-2.jpg\" /></a></div>\r\n<div>Mt knh cong trn sang 2 cnh kh sang trng v cng l c trng ca dng Note, c trang b knh cng lc Corning Gorilla Glass Victus+ gia tng kh nng chng try xc rt tt, cho bn yn tm hn khi s dng my.</div>\r\n<h3>Thi lng s dng c ngy vi vin pin 5000 mAh</h3>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>Vin pin trn Galaxy S22 Ultra 5G c h tr l 5000 mAh tng t nh<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi Samsung Galaxy S21 Ultra ti Thegioididong.com\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/samsung-galaxy-s21-ultra\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Galaxy S21 Ultra 5G</a>nhng cng sut sc th  c nng ln thnh 45 W thay v 25 W. Kh nng<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi c sc nhanh kinh doanh ti Thegioididong.com\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-sac-pin-nhanh\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">sc nhanh</a>n tng vi 30 pht c hn 50% dung lng v mt khong 1 gi 10 pht l y.</div>\r\n<div><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/235838/samsung-galaxy-s22-ultra-12-2.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Galaxy S22 Ultra 5G - Thi gian sc\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/235838/samsung-galaxy-s22-ultra-12-2.jpg\" alt=\"Galaxy S22 Ultra 5G - Thi gian sc\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/235838/samsung-galaxy-s22-ultra-12-2.jpg\" /></a></div>\r\n<div>V th vi dung lng pin cao cng kh nng sc nhanh, th Galaxy S22 Ultra 5G hon ton c th cng bn chinh phc cc ta game, nhng b phim yu thch hoc p ng tt nhu cu lm vic c mt ngy di.</div>\r\n<h3>Chuyn i d liu nhanh chng v tin li</h3>\r\n<div>Ngoi ra,  tri nghim s dng ca khch hng c