iPhone ca mnh.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/153856/iphone-113.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | nh chp vi ch  Night Mode nh chp vi ch  Night Mode\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-113.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | nh chp vi ch  Night Mode nh chp vi ch  Night Mode\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-113.jpg\" /></a>\n\n<em>nh chp vi<a title=\"Tm hiu ch  Night Mode\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/hoi-dap/night-mode-la-gi-diem-khac-nhau-giu-night-mode-va-1197122\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"Tm hiu ch  Night Mode\">ch  Night Mode</a></em>\n\nTheo tri nghim th tnh nng ny hot ng rt hiu qu c bit trong nhng mi trng cc k thiu sng.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/153856/iphone-112.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | nh chp bng camera sau\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-112.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | nh chp bng camera sau\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-112.jpg\" /></a>\n\nKch hot ch  chp m s do iPhone t quyt nh vic ca bn ch cn a my ln v chp, rt n gin.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/153856/iphone-11-.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | nh chp ch  gc siu rng\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-11-.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | nh chp ch  gc siu rng\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-11-.jpg\" /></a>\n\n<em>nh chp ch  gc siu rng</em>\n\nNm nay Apple cng  nng cp  phn gii camera trc nn 12 MP thay v 7 MP nh th h trc .\n\nCamera trc cng c mt tnh nng thng minh, khi bn xoay ngang in thoi n s t kch hot ch  selfie gc rng  bn c th chp vi nhiu ngi hn.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/153856/iphone-111.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | nh selfie bng camera trc\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-111.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | nh selfie bng camera trc\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-111.jpg\" /></a>\n\nNgoi ra Apple cng gii thiu tnh nng quay video slow motion dnh cho camera trc, iu m Apple cha tng trang b cho nhng chic iPhone trc y.\n\nXem thm:<a title=\"nh gi chi tit iPhone 11\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tin-tuc/danh-gia-chi-tiet-apple-iphone-11-iphone-2019-1191805\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"nh gi chi tit iPhone 11\">nh gi chi tit iPhone 11: Ha \'bo t\' hay thnh \'bom xt\'?</a>\n<h3>Hiu nng mnh m hng u th gii</h3>\nMi ln ra<a title=\"Tham kho iPhone kinh doanh ti TopZone thnh vin ca Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.topzone.vn/iphone\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">iPhone</a>mi l mi ln Apple mang n cho ngi dng mt tri nghim v hiu nng \"cha tng c\".\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/153856/iphone-11-tgdd45.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Tri nghim chi game trn iPhone 11\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-11-tgdd45.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Tri nghim chi game trn iPhone 11\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-11-tgdd45.jpg\" /></a>\n\nTrn iPhone 11 mi Apple nng cp con chip ca mnh ln th h<a title=\"Tm hiu v chip Apple A13 Bionic\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/hoi-dap/tim-hieu-ve-chip-apple-a13-bionic-tren-iphone-11-n-1197492\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"Tm hiu v chip Apple A13 Bionic\">Apple A13 Bionic</a>rt mnh m.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/153856/iphone-11-dmx18.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | im hiu nng Antutu Benchmark\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-11-dmx18.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | im hiu nng Antutu Benchmark\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-11-dmx18.jpg\" /></a>\n\nChic iPhone ny cng c nng cp dung lng<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi c RAM 4 GB ti Thegioididong.com\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-ram-4gb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">RAM 4 GB</a>thay v 3 GB nh th h trc .\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/153856/iphone-119.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Tri nghim thao tc\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-119.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Tri nghim thao tc\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-119.jpg\" /></a>\n\n mc cu hnh trn gip<a title=\"Tham kho cc mu in thoi chi game ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-choi-game\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">in thoi chi game</a>tt vi cc ta game ph bin hin nay mt cch mt m, n nh. Mi thao tc trn iPhone mi cng cho tc  phn hi nhanh m bn gn nh s khng cm nhn c s git lag cho d c s dng trong mt thi gian di.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/153856/iphone-11-tgdd4.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Tri nghim chi game\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-11-tgdd4.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Tri nghim chi game\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-11-tgdd4.jpg\" /></a>\n\nXem thm:<a title=\"Th nghim  bn iPhone 11\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tin-tuc/thu-nghiem-do-ben-iphone-11-cao-xuoc-nung-nong-va-be-cong-1203631\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"Th nghim  bn iPhone 11\">Th nghim  bn iPhone 11: Co xc, nung nng v b cong</a>\n\nPhin bn iOS 15 (12/2021) i km vi chic iPhone ny cng c trang b nhiu tnh nng hn gip bn s dng chic iPhone hiu qu hn.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/153856/iphone-112-1.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Thit k thi trang\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-112-1.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Thit k thi trang\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-112-1.jpg\" /></a>\n\nFace ID trn iPhone 11 cng c ci tin  c th nhn din  nhiu gc  hn v tc  phn hi nhanh hn.\n<h3>Nhng thay i v thit k theo hng tch cc</h3>\nChng ta s c mt mt lng hon thin di dng knh v Apple ni rng h  s dng loi knh bn nht t trc ti nay cho chic iPhone ny.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/153856/iphone-113-1.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Thit k cm camera kp  mt sau\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-113-1.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Thit k cm camera kp  mt sau\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-113-1.jpg\" /></a>\n\nCamera kp trn iPhone mi cng c thit k li v tin vui l n s bt li hn so vi trn trn iPhone Xr trc y.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/153856/iphone-115-1.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Thit k thi trang\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-115-1.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Thit k thi trang\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-115-1.jpg\" /></a>\n\nim nhn v cm camera to bn  mt sau s gip ngi khc d dng nhn bit bn ang s dng mt chic iPhone 11 trn tay.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/153856/iphone-118.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Khay sim\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-118.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Khay sim\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-118.jpg\" /></a>\n\nLogo qu to truyn thng ca Apple nay  c di chuyn v phn chnh gia ca mt ln thay v t lch v pha cnh trn nh nhng i iPhone trc .\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/153856/iphone-11-tgdd17.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Kh nng chng nc chun IP68\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-11-tgdd17.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Kh nng chng nc chun IP68\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-11-tgdd17.jpg\" /></a>\n\nApple cho bit h  hon thin trn iPhone mi  n cho kh nng<a title=\"Tham kho gi in thoi smartphone chng nc chng bi\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd?f=chong-nuoc-bui\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">chng nc</a>tt hn v ngi dng c th yn tm v iu .\n<h3>Thi lng pin tt nht t trc ti nay</h3>\nKhi ni n thi lng pin iPhone 11, hn nhiu ngi  c ao rng my s c vin pin tt ging nh iPhone Xr (c thi lng pin tt nht so vi bt k iPhone hin i no).\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/153856/iphone-11-tgdd46.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Thi lng pin\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-11-tgdd46.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Thi lng pin\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-11-tgdd46.jpg\" /></a>\n\nTuy nhin bn s cn c mt chic my thm ch cn tt hn na.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/153856/iphone-116-1.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Thit k hin i\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-116-1.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Thit k hin i\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-116-1.jpg\" /></a>\n\nTheo Apple th chic iPhone mi s c thi lng pin tru hn 1 gi so vi chic iPhone Xr.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/153856/iphone-11-tgdd40.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Giao din Dark Mode\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-11-tgdd40.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Giao din Dark Mode\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-11-tgdd40.jpg\" /></a>\n\nNh vy vi iPhone mi bn hon ton c th s dng my ln ti 2 ngy m khng cn lo lng vic thit b s ht pin gia chng.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/153856/iphone-11-tgdd39.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Thi lng pin\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-11-tgdd39.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Thi lng pin\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-11-tgdd39.jpg\" /></a>\n\nTt nhin my cng s h tr cng ngh<a title=\"Tham kho gi in thoi smartphone sc pin nhanh\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd?f=sac-pin-nhanh\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">sc nhanh</a>nhng bn phi mua thm c sc bn ngoi  c th s dng tnh nng ny.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/153856/iphone-117.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Thi lng s dng di\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-117.jpg\" alt=\"in thoi iPhone 11 64GB | Thi lng s dng di\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/153856/iphone-117.jpg\" /></a>\n\nVi chng  tnh nng, chng  ci tin th chic iPhone 11 ny t tin s l mt i th ng gm vi nhng chic flagship n t cc hng Android ang c mt trn th trng.\n\n</div>', 'in thoi iPhone 11 64GB', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '182-autosave-v1', '', '', '2022-05-15 10:42:55', '2022-05-15 10:42:55', '', 182, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=511', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
