eno7-z-4-2.jpg\" alt=\"Cm camera - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-4-2.jpg\" /></a>\n\nChng ta s c nhng bc nh siu lung linh ch sau 1 ng tc nhn chp nh kh nng<a title=\"Tham kho ng ri chp nh xa phng ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-camera-xoa-phong\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">chp nh chn dung</a>vi tnh nng Bokeh Flare. Phn phng nn s c lm m vi hiu ng tng t cc my nh c DSLR.  chuyn gia cc vng trong hnh rt mt m, khng to cm gic gi to hay b c gng xo nho bng thut ton.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-chup-bokeh.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Bokeh Flare - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-chup-bokeh.jpg\" alt=\"Bokeh Flare - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-chup-bokeh.jpg\" /></a>\n\nVi ch  chn dung mu AI s gip bn tr thnh tm im ca mi bc hnh, ch phn ch th gi li mu sc, phng nn trng en gip cho nh chp ca bn thm phn n tng hn, cng nh c rt nhiu b lc c sn  bn la chn ph hp vi phong cch nh chp.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-bo-loc-mau.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"B lc mu - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-bo-loc-mau.jpg\" alt=\"B lc mu - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-bo-loc-mau.jpg\" /></a>\n\n<em>*nh chp p dng b lc mu</em>\n\nnh gi chung cc bc hnh c chp bi Reno7 Z 5G c  chi tit tt, di nhy sng n, mu sc chn thc nn bn c th chp v ng ti ln cc mng x hi ngay lp tc m khng cn phi qua cc bc chnh sa. Cc tm nh chp m cng c cht lng rt n, nh n rc r khng b chi,  phi sng tt v t b nhiu ht.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-chup-thieu-sang.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"nh chp t camera - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-chup-thieu-sang.jpg\" alt=\"nh chp t camera - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-chup-thieu-sang.jpg\" /></a>\n\nCn v camera trc 16 MP ca OPPO th vn lun ghi c im tuyt i vi nhng tm nh selfie ln da mn mng, mt to long lanh, chi tit mi th u tuyt. Nu bn ngi o qu mc th ch cn h thanh trt lm p xung thp nht th cng  c c bc nh tht t nhin nhng vn c  p lung linh.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-chup-selfie.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"nh chp t camera trc - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-chup-selfie.jpg\" alt=\"nh chp t camera trc - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-chup-selfie.jpg\" /></a>\n\nNgoi ra th chng ta c th s dng tnh nng quay video hin th kp kh l hay, cht lng video cao nht s l 1080p nhng quan trng l c lun tnh nng lm p AI khi quay. Nhng video s khng cn phi qua hu k qu phc tp m c th s dng ngay lp tc.\n<h3><strong>Hiu nng vt bt, phn hi tc thi</strong></h3>\nV hiu nng, OPPO Reno7 Z 5G nm nay  c ci tin khi trang b con chip Snapdragon 695 5G n t nh Qualcomm, y l mt con chip c hiu nng n v c nhiu Hng trang b trn dng sn phm tm trung ca mnh. V mt im s, mnh c kim tra bng phn mm o hiu nng Benchmark (bn tri) v PCMark (bn phi) c kt qu nh sau:\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-5-4.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Kim tra hiu nng bng phn mm - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-5-4.jpg\" alt=\"Kim tra hiu nng bng phn mm - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-5-4.jpg\" /></a>\n\nReno7 Z s hu b nh RAM ln n 13 GB (8 GB mc nh + 5 GB m rng),<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi ROM 128 GB ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-rom-128gb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ROM 128 GB</a>, y cng l mt con s kh n  thi im hin ti (3/2022) v c th p ng tt nhu cu s dng ca hu ht mi i tng ngi dng.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-mo-rong-ram.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Kh nng m rng RAM - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-mo-rong-ram.jpg\" alt=\"Kh nng m rng RAM - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-mo-rong-ram.jpg\" /></a>\n\nCc tc v hng ngy nh lt web, mng x hi, hc, hp online th Reno7 Z cho mt tc  rt n nh, cc thao tc chm, m ng dng c phn hi nhanh. Vi mt con chip hiu nng cao, phn mm c ti u mnh m nn kh nng chi game trn OPPO Reno7 Z 5G cng rt tuyt vi.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-6-2.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Thao tc hng ngy - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-6-2.jpg\" alt=\"Thao tc hng ngy - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-6-2.jpg\" /></a>\n\nKhi o hiu nng vi ta game Lin Qun Mobile th my cho tri nghim game tt, khng tt FPS khi chi  mc FPS cao. Cc thao tc di chuyn mt m, hnh nh trong game cng kh p mt, combat tng n nh, khng c hin tng git, lag hay tt FPS.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-7-2.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Biu  FPS game Lin Qun Mobile - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-7-2.jpg\" alt=\"Biu  FPS game Lin Qun Mobile - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-7-2.jpg\" /></a>\n\nPUBG Mobile cng cho kt qu tng t, bn sng thoi mi, di chuyn nhn vt mt m, FPS n nh khi bt tc  khung hnh Cc cao.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-pubg.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"PUBG Mobile - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-pubg.jpg\" alt=\"PUBG Mobile - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-pubg.jpg\" /></a>\n\nVi Genshin Impact th my chi mt  mc  ha mc nh, tuy nhin  ha cha c chi tit v p mt.\n<h3><strong>Nng cao tri nghim nghe nhn</strong></h3>\nMn hnh Reno7 Z 5G trang b tm nn AMOLED, kch thc 6.43 inch,  phn gii Full HD+ (1080 x 2400 pixel), tn s qut 60 Hz v c bo v bi lp knh cng lc Schott Xensation UP.\n\nV mn hnh th cc thng s trn kh c bn v khng c nhiu ni bt khi so vi th h trc, my vn cho cht lng hin th rt tt vi mu sc ti tn, trong tro, khng b m mu v hin th kh sng ng.  sng mn hnh ti a t 600 nits,  dng trong iu kin sng va phi.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-man-hinh.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Mn hnh hin th sc nt - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-man-hinh.jpg\" alt=\"Mn hnh hin th sc nt - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-man-hinh.jpg\" /></a>\n\nMn hnh ny cn c kh nng bo v mt ca chng ta di tc ng ca nh sng xanh theo tiu chun Thy S.\n<h3>Bc thy tc  vi Super VOOC</h3>\nKh n tng vi thi gian s dng lin tc ca OPPO Reno7 Z 5G khi my t n hn 10 ting, cc tc v mnh s dng cng rt c bn nh chi game, xem phim, mng x hi* v c th l my trang b vin pin c dung lng 4500 mAh.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-8-2.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Thi gian s dng Pin - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-8-2.jpg\" alt=\"Thi gian s dng Pin - OPPO Reno7 Z 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/271717/oppo-reno7-z-8-2.jpg\" /></a>\n\nThi gian sc y vin pin ny ch ri vo khong 75 pht vi sc Super VOOC 33 W, khi cn gp th bn c th cm sc 30 pht th my  c th sc c khong 48% pin.*\n\n<i>*Thi gian sc, s dng c th thay i ty theo nhu cu, tc v s dng.</i>\n\nV pin th y cng l mt con s kh n tng, thi gian sc va  khng qu lu, thi gian s dng th kh di, c th s dng n trong mt ngy.\n\nOPPO Reno7 Z 5G - mt sn phm c thit k cng nh mu sc cc bt mt, camera c u t  mang li hiu ng tng t nh my nh DSLR chuyn nghip, hiu nng c th cng bn x l hu ht mi tc v bn cn cng mt thng s pin n tng. OPPO Reno7 Z 5G ha hn s khuynh o phn khc tm in thoi trung trong thi gian ti.\n\n</div>', 'in thoi OPPO Reno7 Z 5G', '<p><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '180-autosave-v1', '', '', '2022-05-15 13:22:36', '2022-05-15 13:22:36', '', 180, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=516', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
