ng thi gian di khng lo mi tay. My cng s hu cm bin vn tay cnh bn cho vic m kha d dng, mang n s tin li trong qu trnh s dng.\n<h3><strong>Gii tr sng ng cng mn hnh 6.6 inch</strong></h3>\nMc d s hu mn hnh git nc v c phn cm di hi dy, nhng Realme C35 li s hu mn hnh ln kch thc ln n 6.6 inch vi  phn gii Full HD+, mang ti mt cht lng hnh nh chi tit, sc nt, mu sc sng ng.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/261888/realme-c35-11-2.jpg\"><img class=\" ls-is-cached lazyloaded\" title=\"Realme C35 - Gii tr sng ng cng mn hnh 6.6 inch\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/261888/realme-c35-11-2.jpg\" alt=\"Realme C35 - Gii tr sng ng cng mn hnh 6.6 inch\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/261888/realme-c35-11-2.jpg\" /></a>\n\nTm nn IPS trn Realme C35, mnh c cm gic l nh sn xut y tone mu ln gip cho di mu ca my trng ti hn. Khi m mnh lt Tiktok th cht lng hin th, mu sc kh l ti v nnh mt. c bit l nhng video c cc ni dung nhiu mu sc nh cc MV Kpop th chc chn s cc k ng .\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/261888/realme-c35-12-2.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Realme C35 - Tm nn IPS trn Realme C35\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/261888/realme-c35-12-2.jpg\" alt=\"Realme C35 - Tm nn IPS trn Realme C35\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/261888/realme-c35-12-2.jpg\" /></a>\n\nHn na  sng 600 nits cho cht lng hin th kh tt  ngoi tri, khi mnh nghing mn hnh nh qua cc gc cht lng hnh nh hin th cng khng b bin i qu nhiu.\n<h3><strong>Ghi li trn vn hnh nh sng ng</strong></h3>\nRealme C35 c camera trc 8 MP, cho cht lng hnh nh selfie n nh, nu ch ni v mu sc th kh tt, ti to mu sc rt n nhng  m ni v  chi tit th con ny vn cha ti to c nhiu chi tit v b bt mt s ch trn hnh.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/261888/realme-c35-16.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Realme C35 - Camera trc 8 MP\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/261888/realme-c35-16.jpg\" alt=\"Realme C35 - Camera trc 8 MP\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/261888/realme-c35-16.jpg\" /></a>\n\nTrang b camera chnh 50 MP mang li nhng bc nh r nt hn, chi tit hn vi  phn gii cao, khng s b b nh ngay c khi bn zoom ln rt nhiu ln.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/261888/realme-c35-3.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Realme C35 - Camera chnh 50 MP\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/261888/realme-c35-3.jpg\" alt=\"Realme C35 - Camera chnh 50 MP\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/261888/realme-c35-3.jpg\" /></a>\n\nNhng bc nh khi chp ngoi tri cho ra cht lng tng i rt tt, kh nng ti to mu sc n. Nhng m mt s hnh nh s c y tone mu ln mt cht, th ci ny vn s li tu thuc vo s thch ca mi ngi, c bn s thch mu sc n ti hn, sc s hn  khng phi chnh li mu sc na, cn mt s bn th thch mu sc n phi chn thc hn.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/261888/realme-c35-10-2.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Realme C35 - Bc nh khi chp ngoi tri\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/261888/realme-c35-10-2.jpg\" alt=\"Realme C35 - Bc nh khi chp ngoi tri\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/261888/realme-c35-10-2.jpg\" /></a>\n\nKhi chuyn qua vi ch  chp nh ban m, Realme C35  lm kh tt, cc vng ti c y sng ln mt mc, cc nh n khng b lo qu nhiu, duy nht ch c mt im  l v  chi tit th vn cn hi b m mt vi ch.\n\nCn khi mnh chuyn sang chp ngi vi ch  chn dung th hnh nh c phn r gia ch th v nn  ng sau, cc chi tit vn c hin ln y . Nhn chung th vi<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi ang bn ti thegioididong.com\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">in thoi</a>gi di 4 triu th cng gi l n p trong tm gi.\n<h3><strong>Hiu nng n nh phc v tt cc tc v</strong></h3>\nV cu hnh mu smartphone ny c trang b con chip x l UNISOC T616 cho hiu nng n nh, mt m vi cc tc v hng ngy cng nh ci thin hiu sut  tri nghim chi game tt hn.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/261888/realme-c35-5.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Realme C35 - Hiu nng n nh phc v tt cc tc v\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/261888/realme-c35-5.jpg\" alt=\"Realme C35 - Hiu nng n nh phc v tt cc tc v\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/261888/realme-c35-5.jpg\" /></a>\n\nKhi chi Lin qun, do l my h tr bt c FPS cao cho nn l khung hnh m mnh  c o c  mc 60 FPS, c khi cn vt qua c ngng 60 FPS lun. Hn na tri nghim thc t i vi mnh l tng i n vi cht lng  ho cao, chi game xy ra hin tng git lag th cng t, khng c gp thng xuyn v quan trng hn ht  l my chi rt mt v n nh.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/261888/realme-c35-18.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Realme C35 - Test game Lin Qun\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/261888/realme-c35-18.jpg\" alt=\"Realme C35 - Test game Lin Qun\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/261888/realme-c35-18.jpg\" /></a>\n\nCn v pha game PUBG Mobile th vi mc  ho HD, tc  khung hnh cao th FPS m mnh c o c hi thp so vi k vng ca mnh v n ch khong 29 - 32 FPS. i lc trong mt s tnh hung xy ra giao tranh th n s xy ra git lag nh, nn  c th chi game c mt m hn th mnh s chn cch gim  ho xung cht xu th s tt hn.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/261888/realme-c35-17.jpeg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Realme C35 - Test game PUBG\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/261888/realme-c35-17.jpeg\" alt=\"Realme C35 - Test game PUBG\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/261888/realme-c35-17.jpeg\" /></a>\n\nNgoi ra, my cn c cung cp<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi RAM 4 GB ang bn ti thegioididong.com\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-ram-4gb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">RAM 4 GB</a>cho tri nghim a nhim tng i mt,<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi ROM 4 GB ang bn ti thegioididong.com\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-rom-64gb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">b nh trong 64 GB</a>v h tr th nh ngoi ln n 256 GB cho ngi dng cn mt dung lng ln hn  s dng lu di.\n<h3><strong>Dung lng pin ln, h tr sc nhanh</strong></h3>\nMt im m mnh cng kh n tng vi Realme C35  l dung lng pin tng i cao ln ti 5000 mAh. Mc dung lng ny mnh c th s dng gn nh mt ngy cho cc tc v c bn nh lt web, nghe gi m khng cn np li nng lng cho thit b.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/261888/realme-c35-4.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Realme C35 - Dung lng pin ln, h tr sc nhanh\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/261888/realme-c35-4.jpg\" alt=\"Realme C35 - Dung lng pin ln, h tr sc nhanh\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/261888/realme-c35-4.jpg\" /></a>\n\nNgoi dung lng pin khng th Realme C35 cn c h tr<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi c sc nhanh ang bn ti thegioididong.com\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-sac-pin-nhanh\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">sc nhanh</a>cng sut ti 18 W, th mnh mt ti 2h13 l c th sc y li c, p ng ti a nhu cu s dng. Ngoi ra, khi bt ch  siu tit kim pin, n s gip p ng y  nhu cu s dng in thoi ca bn ngay c khi thit b ch cn 5%.\n\nRealme C35 s hu thit k c o vi mu sc tr trung, dung lng pin cao v b 3 camera cht lng, y s l yu t ha hn mang ti nhng tri nghim tuyt vi nht n cho bn.\n\n</div>', 'in thoi Realme C35 64GB', 'Cc sn phm dng da t Php lun c cc nng tin tng, ngay c nhng bn kh tnh nht bi cht lng v  an ton, do c kim nh v cng gt gao.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '178-autosave-v1', '', '', '2022-05-15 13:26:44', '2022-05-15 13:26:44', '', 178, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=519', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
