in nay, vi tc v ny i lc thao tc di chuyn c  tr tuy nhin khng ng k, mu sc n nhng chi tit hin th  ha t  mc kh.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/251856/samsung-galaxy-a03-5.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Chi game lin qun | Samsung Galaxy A03\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251856/samsung-galaxy-a03-5.jpg\" alt=\"Chi game lin qun | Samsung Galaxy A03\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251856/samsung-galaxy-a03-5.jpg\" /></a>\n\nMy c th bt 60 FPS t xy ra hin tng drop v git lag. Mnh kh l bt ng vi iu ny khi tri nghim trn mt con my trong phn khc gi r. Sau khi chi 1, 2 trn mnh thy my ch m nh  mt lng.\n\nNhn chung, v cc tc v nh hng ngy th Galaxy A03 vn p ng va  nhu cu ca mnh, nhng cn chi game nng thng xuyn th mnh ngh y cha phi l mt s la chn hon ho.\n<h3>Khng gian gii tr ln</h3>\nGalaxy A03 s dng mn hnh git nc Infinity-V quen thuc, c kch thc 6.5 inch,  phn gii HD+ trn tm nn IPS. Phn mn hnh ny cho mnh mt khng gian gii tr rng ri, c th hin th nhiu thng tin hn khi m mnh lt Facebook, lt web hay xem phim.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/251856/samsung-galaxy-a03-6.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Mn hnh git nc | Samsung Galaxy A03\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251856/samsung-galaxy-a03-6.jpg\" alt=\"Mn hnh git nc | Samsung Galaxy A03\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251856/samsung-galaxy-a03-6.jpg\" /></a>\n\nMu sc hin th tng i ti, gc nhn tm,  sng ca my khng qu cao vn c th s dng trong iu kin ngoi tri.\n\nNgoi ra, chic in thoi ny cn h tr cng ngh m thanh Dolby Atmos, cho bn tri nghim m thanh mt cch trn vn v tt hn, nng cao kh nng gii tr ca my, tuy nhin cng ngh ny ch hot ng khi kt ni vi tai nghe h tr m thanh ni hoc loa.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/251856/samsung-galaxy-a03-10.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"H tr cng ngh m thanh Dolby Atmos | Samsung Galaxy A03\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251856/samsung-galaxy-a03-10.jpg\" alt=\"H tr cng ngh m thanh Dolby Atmos | Samsung Galaxy A03\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251856/samsung-galaxy-a03-10.jpg\" /></a>\n<h3>Camera c  phn gii cao trong phn khc</h3>\nGalaxy A03 l smartphone gi r u tin ca Samsung s hu camera chnh 48 MP khu  F1.8, cng vi  l camera xa phng 2 MP gip to ra cc bc nh vi kh nng tp trung vo ch th v xa phng tng i tt.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/251856/samsung-galaxy-a03-7.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Camera c  phn gii cao | Samsung Galaxy A03\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251856/samsung-galaxy-a03-7.jpg\" alt=\"Camera c  phn gii cao | Samsung Galaxy A03\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251856/samsung-galaxy-a03-7.jpg\" /></a>\n\nNhng bc nh trong iu kin  sng cho chi tit tt, mu sc th hin ti hn so vi thc t. Cc ch  chp m, chp thiu sng my vn ti hin chi tit y  tuy nhin vn b nhe  mt s ch th nht nh.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/251856/samsung-galaxy-a03-8.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"nh chp t camera | Samsung Galaxy A03\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251856/samsung-galaxy-a03-8.jpg\" alt=\"nh chp t camera | Samsung Galaxy A03\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251856/samsung-galaxy-a03-8.jpg\" /></a>\n\nBn cnh  camera trc c  phn gii 5 MP tch hp sn lot b lc c o v lm p.\n\nXem thm:<a title=\"nh gi chi tit Camera Samsung Galaxy A03\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tin-tuc/dao-choi-khap-cac-cho-hoa-sai-gon-cung-galaxy-a03-1413162\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">nh gi chi tit camera | Do chi khp cc ch hoa Si Gn cng Galaxy A03</a>\n<h3>Pin ln thoi mi s dng c ngy di</h3>\nCui cng v phn pin my s hu dung lng 5000 mAh, y l mt dung lng pin kh tru, c th p ng c nhu cu s dng cho mt ngy di vi nhu cu c bn hng ngy.\n\nSau khi tri qua bi nh gi pin ca Th Gii Di ng th my tr n hn 9 ting, mt con s khng h t. m bo tri nghim s dng thit b ca bn m khng lo b gin on.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/251856/samsung-galaxy-a03-9.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Thi gian s dng Pin | Samsung Galaxy A03\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251856/samsung-galaxy-a03-9.jpg\" alt=\"Thi gian s dng Pin | Samsung Galaxy A03\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251856/samsung-galaxy-a03-9.jpg\" /></a>\n\nTuy nhin my s khng c trang b sc nhanh m ch c cng sut 7.75 W nn thi gian sc y li pin kh lu. Nhng nhn li, dng mt ngy v sc li th thi lng pin trn Galaxy A03 chnh l mt im cng ln ca chic my ny.\n\nSamsung Galaxy A03 c thit k mt lng vn nhm p mt cng mt mn hnh mu sc ti tn. Camera c  chi tit cao p ng c nhu cu chp nh c bn v mt vin pin tru b. Nu bn ang cn mt chic smartphone lm my ph hoc nhu cu s dng khng qu cao nh c bo, gii tr nh nhng hay phc v cho vic hc online th y chnh l mt s la chn rt ph hp.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'in thoi Samsung Galaxy A03 3GB', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '174-autosave-v1', '', '', '2022-05-15 13:54:35', '2022-05-15 13:54:35', '', 174, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=525', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
