(529, 2, '2022-05-15 14:19:26', '2022-05-15 14:19:26', '<div style=\"height: 400px; white-space: pre-wrap; overflow: auto;\">\n<h3><strong><a title=\"Tham kho thng tin sn phm ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G</a>mang trong mnh kh nhiu nhng nng cp cc k sng gi. L chic<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi kinh doanh ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">in thoi</a>c mn hnh ln, tn s qut 120 Hz, hiu nng n nh cng mt vin pin siu tru.</strong></h3>\n<h3><strong>Thit k cng cp, cm nm rt m tay</strong></h3>\nim ni bt  phn thit k ca Redmi Note 11 Pro chnh l cm camera kh ln v li so vi mt lng, mt lng c cht liu bng knh  c lm phng i. Khung vin bng nha cng c bo trn v vt phng rt lin mch, mc  hon thin tt, khng c hin tng p p khi mnh s dng chic my ny.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-2-1.jpg\"><img class=\" ls-is-cached lazyloaded\" title=\"Khung vin phng - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-2-1.jpg\" alt=\"Khung vin phng - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-2-1.jpg\" /></a>\n\nMt trc chng ta s c mt camera selfie dng c l t  gia phn mn hnh. Cnh vin c phm tng gim m lng, phm ngun tch hp cm bin vn tay cho tc  nhn din nhanh chng v c t  v tr kh d thao tc.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-15.jpg\"><img class=\" ls-is-cached lazyloaded\" title=\"Cnh vin - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-15.jpg\" alt=\"Cnh vin - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-15.jpg\" /></a>\n\nCnh di c trang b mt dy loa, micro, khe sim cng vi cng sc Type C thng thy trn cc sn phm hin nay.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-4-1.jpg\"><img class=\" ls-is-cached lazyloaded\" title=\"Cnh di - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-4-1.jpg\" alt=\"Cnh di - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-4-1.jpg\" /></a>\n<h3><strong>Hiu nng n nh cho mi tc v</strong></h3>\n<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi Xiaomi kinh doanh ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-xiaomi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Xiaomi</a>trang b cho Note 11 Pro b vi x l<a title=\"Tham kho thng tin CPU G96\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tin-tuc/mediatek-ra-mat-helio-g96-helio-g88-1368559\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Mediatek Helio G96 8 nhn</a>mnh m. y l con chip thuc dng G chuyn Game nn c th gip cho chng ta c th x l trn tru hu ht cc tc v c bn hng ngy cng nh l mt s ta game nh nhng cho n nhng game yu cu  ha.\n\nMnh c kim tra bng phn mm o hiu nng Benchmark (bn tri) v c kt qu im n nhn 495, im a nhn 1640, PCMark (bn phi) t 9125 im.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-5-1.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"o sc mnh bng phn mm - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-5-1.jpg\" alt=\"o sc mnh bng phn mm - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-5-1.jpg\" /></a>\n\n<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi c 8 GB RAM kinh doanh ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-xiaomi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">RAM 8 GB</a>l mt con s n trong thi im hin nay, my c th a nhim n, t xy ra hin tng git lag khi mnh bt nhiu ng dng.\n\nMy cng c trang b cng ngh tn nhit LiquidCool a chiu mi, gip tn nhit mt cch kh hiu qu. Mnh c tri nghim thc t khi mnh chi 2 ta game quen thuc l Lin Qun v PUBG Mobile v c mt s thng tin sau:\n\nVi Lin Qun, my c phn  ha mt, n nh. T khu chn tng cho n lc vo trn my t xy ra hin tng git lag. Lc bt u combat my khng xy ra hin tng drop FPS v lun c mc FPS n nh l 60. Sau khi chi tm 15 pht my s kh nng  phn mt lng, gn cm camera.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-6-1.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Lin Qun Mobile - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-6-1.jpg\" alt=\"Lin Qun Mobile - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-6-1.jpg\" /></a>\n\nCn v PUBG Mobile, khi mnh bt mc  ha HD tc  khung hnh cao, my cho ra mt ci tri nghim cha n. Khung hnh cn kh l git lag  mc 30 FPS c tnh trng b tt xung mc 26, 27 FPS, di chuyn nhn vt hay thao tc nht  cn kh kh, lc giao tranh cha chun xc cho lm.\n\nKhi mnh chuyn qua mc  ha Cn bng vi tc  khung hnh Cc cao my hu nh gii quyt c cc vn  trn.  ho n nh, vo u sng thao tc kh mt, di chuyn hay i sng nht  khng cn git lag v n nh  mc 40 FPS.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-7-1.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"PUBG Mobile - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-7-1.jpg\" alt=\"PUBG Mobile - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-7-1.jpg\" /></a>\n<h3><strong>Khng gian hin th ln, tn s qut 120 Hz mt m</strong></h3>\nXiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro c mt chic mn hnh kch thc kh ln ln n 6.67 inch, s dng tm nn AMOLED cho ra cht lng hin th n, mu sc ti v  chi tit cao vi  phn gii Full HD+,  tng phn tng i cao v nnh mt.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-8-1.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Mn hnh rc r - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-8-1.jpg\" alt=\"Mn hnh rc r - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-8-1.jpg\" /></a>\n\nKch thc mn hnh ln kt hp vi phn vin mn hnh c lm mng hn mang li khng gian hin th rng ri, h tr cng vic cng nh gii tr s tt hn, hin th mt lc nhiu thng tin hn.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-9-1.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Vin mn hnh mng - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-9-1.jpg\" alt=\"Vin mn hnh mng - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-9-1.jpg\" /></a>\n\nNgoi ra, Redmi Note 11 Pro cn h tr di mu rng DCI-P3, ch  bo v mt, tri nghim gii tr chi game lt web u mt m nh vo vic my c trang b tn s qut 120 Hz cng l mt im cng ln trn phin bn ln ny.\n<h3><strong>Camera AI n 108 MP</strong></h3>\nCamera trn Redmi Note 11 Pro cng kh n tng khi my c trang b  mt sau cm 4 camera AI, cm bin chnh 108 MP, camera gc siu rng 8 MP, camera o chiu su 2 MP v camera macro 2 MP.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-10-1.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Camera n 108 MP - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-10-1.jpg\" alt=\"Camera n 108 MP - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-10-1.jpg\" /></a>\n\nVi camera 108 MP trong iu kin  sng my cho ra nhng bc nh v cng l chi tit, mu sc ti, ti hin li gn nh l hon ho v y  chi tit, khng b bt mu.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-13-1.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"nh chp t camera chnh - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-13-1.jpg\" alt=\"nh chp t camera chnh - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-13-1.jpg\" /></a>\n\nNhng bc nh trong iu kin chp m hay l chp thiu sng th cht lng nh cho ra cng  c ci thin hn kh nhiu, chi tit c ti hin gn nh l y  v nhng phn qu ti s c nng sng hn  gip cho tng th bc nh tr nn hi ha hn v hn ch c tnh trng b nhiu nh.\n\nCn v phn chp chn dung my cng lm kh tt khi phn ch th gn nh l c tch khng b lem v gip cho phn ch th ca bc nh trng s ni bt hn rt l nhiu.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-14.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"nh chp xa phng - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-14.jpg\" alt=\"nh chp xa phng - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-14.jpg\" /></a>\n\n mt trc c mt chic camera selfie dng c l  phn gii 16 MP gip cho ra nhng bc nh chp kh l chi tit, da ch th tr ln hng ho v ti tn hn kh nhiu.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-12-1.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"nh chp selfie - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-12-1.jpg\" alt=\"nh chp selfie - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-12-1.jpg\" /></a>\n<h3><strong>Pin ln, sc siu nhanh</strong></h3>\nXiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G trang b mt dung lng pin kh l tru l 5000 mAh cng vi cng sut sc n 67 W. Mnh c s dng qua nhng ci tc v chi game, lt web, xem YouTube hay nhng ci tc v hng ngy khc mt cch xen k nhau th my c thi gian s dng l 9 ting 43 pht.*\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-11-1.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Thi gian s dng Pin - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-11-1.jpg\" alt=\"Thi gian s dng Pin - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro 4G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/270471/xiaomi-redmi-note-11-pro-4g-11-1.jpg\" /></a>\n\nVi cng sut sc cao nh vy th khi m mnh sc t 0 - 100% cng ch mt khong 55 pht*. iu ny gip cho nhng hot ng gii tr cng nh l lm vic, hc tp vi chic Redmi Note 11 Pro trong 1 ngy s khng b gin on.\n\n*Thi gian s dng c th chnh lch ty theo nhu cu, tc v s dng.\n\nXiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro vi nhng ci im sng nh l mn hnh ln, cht lng hin th sc nt, mt thi lng pin s dng lu cng vi tc  sc cc k nhanh chng, camera n, hiu nng mt m th mnh ngh y s l mt ng c vin kh nng k trong phn khc tm trung so vi cc i th khc trong cng tm gi.\n\n</div>', 'in thoi Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '165-autosave-v1', '', '', '2022-05-15 14:19:26', '2022-05-15 14:19:26', '', 165, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=529', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
