(533, 2, '2022-05-16 06:59:25', '2022-05-16 06:59:25', '<div style=\"height: 400px; white-space: pre-wrap; overflow: auto;\">\n<h3><strong>Ti s kin ra mt sn phm mi din ra hm 29/3,<a title=\"Xiaomi\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-xiaomi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"Xiaomi\">Xiaomi</a> ra mt<a title=\"Xiaomi Redmi Note 11S 5G\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/xiaomi-redmi-note-11s-5g\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"Xiaomi Redmi Note 11S 5G\">Xiaomi Redmi Note 11S 5G</a>ton cu. Thit b l mt bn nng cp ng gi so vi<a title=\"Redmi Note 11S 4G\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/xiaomi-redmi-note-11s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"Redmi Note 11S 4G\">Redmi Note 11S 4G</a>, cng xem my c g c bit thi no.</strong></h3>\n<h3><strong>Thit k quen thuc nhng vn thi thng</strong></h3>\nRedmi Note 11S 5G c ngoi hnh bt mt vi3 mu sc thi thng gm: Midnight Black, Twilight Blue v Star Blue. Vin mn hnh hai bn ca my kh mng cng vi  l cnh vin bo cong theo lng bn tay, to cm gic cm nm thoi mi hn.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/272668/xiaomi-redmi-note-11s-5g-310322-121248.jpeg\"><img class=\" ls-is-cached lazyloaded\" title=\"Thit k thi thng - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11S 5G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/272668/xiaomi-redmi-note-11s-5g-310322-121248.jpeg\" alt=\"Thit k thi thng - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11S 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/272668/xiaomi-redmi-note-11s-5g-310322-121248.jpeg\" /></a>\n\nMn hnh ca Redmi Note 11S 5G c tm nnIPS LCD vi kch thc 6.6 inch cng tc  lm ti 90 Hz. Cha ht, cm camera thit k dc to im nhn kh n tng cho mt sau, ngi dng cng s bt gp logo Redmi  gc tri bn di ca my.\n<h3><strong>Hiu nng n nh vi chip Dimensity 810 5G</strong></h3>\nCc sn phm Xiaomi khng bao gi lm chng ta tht vng v cu hnh v Redmi Note 11S 5G cng khng ngoi l. Vi con chip Mediatek Dimensity 810 5G, ngi dng s thoi mi chi game, xem phim, lt web v cc tc v khc m khng lo git lag.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/272668/xiaomi-redmi-note-11s-5g-310322-121253.jpeg\"><img class=\" ls-is-cached lazyloaded\" title=\"Hiu nng n nh - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11S 5G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/272668/xiaomi-redmi-note-11s-5g-310322-121253.jpeg\" alt=\"Hiu nng n nh - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11S 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/272668/xiaomi-redmi-note-11s-5g-310322-121253.jpeg\" /></a>\n\nBn cng s nhn c vin pin 5000 mAh i km sc nhanh 33 W, thng s ny c th gip bn s dng my lin tc trong 1 ngy, thm ch c th ln n 2 ngy nu bn s dng khng thng xuyn.\n<h3><strong>Camera phc v yu cu chp nh c bn</strong></h3>\nRedmi Note 11S 5G s hu cm 3 camera sau, trong  cm bin chnh c  phn gii 50 MP, 1 camerasiu rng 8 MP v camera macro 2 MP. Vi cm camera ny, bn c th tho thch ghi li nhng khonh khc th v trong cuc sng.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/272668/xiaomi-redmi-note-11s-5g-310322-121246.jpeg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Camera phc v yu cu chp nh c bn - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11S 5G\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/272668/xiaomi-redmi-note-11s-5g-310322-121246.jpeg\" alt=\"Camera phc v yu cu chp nh c bn - Xiaomi Redmi Note 11S 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/272668/xiaomi-redmi-note-11s-5g-310322-121246.jpeg\" /></a>\n\nRedmi Note 11S 5G l mt thit b kh tt vi hiu nng n nh, thit k p v c bit c h tr 5G. Nhn chung, y s l mt la chn thch hp cho bn  phn khc tm trung.\n\n</div>', 'in thoi Xiaomi Redmi Note 11S 5G', 'MIN PH n hng cho n hng trn 200k chuyn tin trc.MIN PH n hng khi mua 2 sn phm nh hn 20g.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '162-autosave-v1', '', '', '2022-05-16 06:59:25', '2022-05-16 06:59:25', '', 162, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=533', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
