(536, 2, '2022-05-16 07:07:26', '2022-05-16 07:07:26', '<div style=\"height: 400px; white-space: pre-wrap; overflow: auto;\">\n<h3><strong><a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/iphone-13-pro-max\">in thoiiPhone 13 Pro Max 128 GB</a>- siu phm c mong ch nht  na cui nm 2021 n t<a title=\"Tham kho gi in thoi smartphone iPhone chnh hng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/apple\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Apple</a>. My c thit k khng my t ph khi so vi ngi tin nhim, bn trong y vn l mt sn phm c mn hnh siu p, tn s qut c nng cp ln 120 Hz mt m, cm bin camera c kch thc ln hn, cng hiu nng mnh m vi sc mnh n t Apple A15 Bionic, sn sng cng bn chinh phc mi th thch.</strong></h3>\n<h3><strong>Thit k ng cp hng u</strong></h3>\niPhone mi k tha thit k c trng tiPhone 12 Pro Max khi s hu khung vin vung vc, mt lng knh cng mn hnh tai th trn vin nm  pha trc.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-3.jpg\"><img class=\" ls-is-cached lazyloaded\" title=\"Thit k vung vc c trng - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-3.jpg\" alt=\"Thit k vung vc c trng - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-3.jpg\" /></a>\n\nVi iPhone 13 Pro Max phn tai th  c thu gn li 20% so vi th h trc, khng ch gii phng nhiu khng gian hin th hn m cn gip mt trc chic<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi kinh doanh ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">in thoi</a>tr nn hp dn hn m vn m bo c hot ng ca cc cm bin.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-2.jpg\"><img class=\" ls-is-cached lazyloaded\" title=\"Mn hnh tai th c tinh gin - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-2.jpg\" alt=\"Mn hnh tai th c tinh gin - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-2.jpg\" /></a>\n\nim thay i d dng nhn bit trn iPhone 13 Pro Max chnh la kch thc ca cm bin camera sau c lm to hn v  tng  nhn din cho sn phm mi th Apple cng  b sung mt ty chn mu scSierra Blue (mu xanh dng nht hn so vi Pacific Blue ca iPhone 12 Pro Max).\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-9.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Sierra Blue tr trung, thanh lch - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-9.jpg\" alt=\"Sierra Blue tr trung, thanh lch - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-9.jpg\" /></a>\n\nMy vn tip tc s dng khung vin thp cao cp cho kh nng chng try xc v va p mt cch vt tri, kt hp vi kha nng khng bui, ncchun IP68.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-4.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Vin thp cao cp - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-4.jpg\" alt=\"Vin thp cao cp - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-4.jpg\" /></a>\n<h3><strong>Mn hnh gii tr siu mt cng tn s qut 120 Hz</strong></h3>\niPhone 13 Pro Max c trang b mn hnh kch thc 6.7 inch cng  phn gii 1284 x 2778 Pixels, s dng tm nn OLED cng cng ngh Super Retina XDR cho kh nng tit kim nng lng vt tri nhng vn m bo hin th sc nt sng ng chn thc.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-5.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Mn hnh kch thc 6.7 inch - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-5.jpg\" alt=\"Mn hnh kch thc 6.7 inch - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-5.jpg\" /></a>\n\niPhone Pro Max nm nay  c nng cp ln tn s qut 120 Hz, mi thao tc chuyn cnh khi lt ngn tay trn mn hnh tr nn mt m hn ng thi hiu ng th gic khi chng ta chi game hoc xem video cng cc k mn nhn.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-6.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Tc  lm ti mn hnh - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-6.jpg\" alt=\"Tc  lm ti mn hnh - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-6.jpg\" /></a>\n\nCng cng ngh ProMotion thng minh c th thay i tn s qut t 10 n 120 ln mi giy ty thuc vo ng dng, thao tc bn ang s dng, nhm ti u thi lng s dng pin v tri nghim ca bn.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-1.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Cng ngh ProMotion thng minh - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-1.jpg\" alt=\"Cng ngh ProMotion thng minh - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-1.jpg\" /></a>\n\nNu bn dng iPhone 13 Pro Max  chi game, tn s qut 120 Hz kt hp hiu sut  ha tuyt vi ca GPU s khin my tr nn v cng hon ho khi tri nghim.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-8.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Mang n tri nghim mt m - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-8.jpg\" alt=\"Mang n tri nghim mt m - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-8.jpg\" /></a>\n\nNgoi ra my cng h tr cng ngh True Tone, di mu rng chun in nh P3 s cho mi tri nghim ca bn trn my tr nn n tng hn bao gi ht.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-20.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Di mu chun in nh P3 - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-20.jpg\" alt=\"Di mu chun in nh P3 - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-20.jpg\" /></a>\n<h3><strong>Cm camera c nng cp ton din</strong></h3>\niPhone 13 Pro Max vn se co b camera 3 ng kinh xp xen ke thanh mt cum vung, t  goc trn bn trai cua lng may gm camera telephoto, camera goc siu rngv camera chnh gc rng vi khu  f/1.5 siu ln.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-21.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Cm camera chuyn nghip - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-21.jpg\" alt=\"Cm camera chuyn nghip - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-21.jpg\" /></a>\n\nCamera gc siu rng cng c nng cp vi khu  f/1.8, cm bin nhanh hn, mang ti nhng bc nh gc siu rng t nhin v chn thc v cn tng cng c kh nng ly nt  khong cch ch 2 cm, mang n tnh nng chp nh quay phim macro y th v.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-10.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Ly nt  khong cch 2cm - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-10.jpg\" alt=\"Ly nt  khong cch 2cm - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-10.jpg\" /></a>\n\nCamera tele trn iPhone 13 Pro Max c th zoom quang hc 3x, phng to hnh nh v video gp 3 ln nhng vn gi nguyn cht lng, h tr chp nh chn dung<a title=\"Tham kho gi in thoi smartphone camera chp hnh xo phng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-camera-xoa-phong\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">xa phng</a>, tch hp sn rt nhiu b lc mu t nhin gip c c bc nh ng nh  mun.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-11.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Kh nng zoom quang hc - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-11.jpg\" alt=\"Kh nng zoom quang hc - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-11.jpg\" /></a>\n\nBn cnh , cm bin LiDAR vn se hin din trn iPhone 13 Pro Max nhm mang n trai nghim thc t tng cng (AR) tt nht cho tt ca ngi dung cng nh h tr cho cm camera ly nt trong mi trng nh sng yu.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-12.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Ly nt trong mi trng anh sng yu - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-12.jpg\" alt=\"Ly nt trong mi trng anh sng yu - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-12.jpg\" /></a>\n\nApple cn tng cng kh nng nhip nh trn iPhone 13 Pro Max vi ch  quay phim chun in nh Cinematicgip ngi dng c th d dng ly nt vo ch th c trong v sau khi quay, ng thi lm m hu cnh v nhng nhn vt khc trong khung hnh.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-13.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Ch  quay Cinematic - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-13.jpg\" alt=\"Ch  quay Cinematic - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-13.jpg\" /></a>\n\ny cng l chic in thoi thng minh u tin cung cp quy trnh lm vic chuyn nghip \"end-to-end\"cho php bn ghi v chnh sa video  nh dng nn ProRes hoc Dolby Vision vi nhiu thit lp chuyn sutogip rt ngn ng k qu trnh hu k to nn nhng thc phim cht lng ng kinh ngc ngay trn chnh chic in thoi ca mnh.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-14.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Kh nng quay video chuyn nghip - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-14.jpg\" alt=\"Kh nng quay video chuyn nghip - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-14.jpg\" /></a>\n<h3><strong>Hiu nng y ha hn vi Apple A15 Bionic</strong></h3>\niPhone 13 Pro Max s c trang b b vi x l Apple A15 Bionic mi nht ca hng, c sn xut trn tin trnh 5 nm, m bo mang li hiu nng vn hnh n tng m vn tit kim in tt nht cung kha nng h tr mang 5G tc  siu cao.\n\nTheo Apple cng b, A15 Bionic l chipset nhanh nht trong th gii smartphone (9/2021), ctc  nhanh hn 50% so vi cc chip khc trn th trng, c th thc hin 15.8 nghn t php tnh mi giy, gip hiu nng CPU nhanh hn bao gi ht.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-15.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Vi x l Apple A15 Bionic - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-15.jpg\" alt=\"Vi x l Apple A15 Bionic - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-15.jpg\" /></a>\n\nMy s hu b nh trong 128 GB, va  vi nhu cu s dng ca mt ngi dng c bn, khng c nhu cu quay video qu nhiu, ngoi ra nm nay cng c thm phin bn b nh trong ln n 1TB, bn c th cn nhc nu c nhu cu lu tr cao.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-16.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Dung lng b nh - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-16.jpg\" alt=\"Dung lng b nh - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-16.jpg\" /></a>\n\nNgoi ra, my cn c tch hp cng ngh Wi-Fi 6, chun kt ni khng dy mi vi vic trang b nhiu bng tn 5G, tng thch vi nhiu nh mng  cc quc gia khc nhau, iPhone 13 Pro Max lun cho tc  mng ti a, cho tri nghim xem phim 4K mt m, ti tp tin trong chp mt, chi game online khng  tr  bt c u.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-17.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Kt ni nhanh chng - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-17.jpg\" alt=\"Kt ni nhanh chng - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-17.jpg\" /></a>\n<h3><strong>Bc nhy vt v thi lng pin</strong></h3>\niPhone Pro Max nh du bc ngot mi trong thi lng pin s dng. Vi vin pin dung lng pin ln kt hp cng mn hnh mi v b vi x l Apple A15 Bionic tit kim in, gip iPhone 13 Pro Max tr thnh chic iPhone c thi lng pin tt nht t trc n nay, di hn 2.5 gi so vi ngi tin nhim.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-18.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Chip A15 gip ti u ha nng lng - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-18.jpg\" alt=\"Chip A15 gip ti u ha nng lng - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-18.jpg\" /></a>\n\nng tic l dung lng pin ca cc mu iPhone mi c ci thin nhng tc  sc nhanh ca chng vn ch dng  mc 20 W qua kt ni c dy v sc qua MagSafe  mc ti a 15 W hoc c th qua b sc khng dy da trn Qi vi cng sut 7.5 W.\n\n<a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-19.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Sc MagSafe - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-19.jpg\" alt=\"Sc MagSafe - iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/230529/iphone-13-pro-max-19.jpg\" /></a>\n\nApple  khng ngng ci tin em n cho ngi dng sn phm tt nht, iPhone 13 Pro Max 128GB vn gi c cc im ni bt ca ngi tin nhim, ni bt vi ci tin v cu h