\"></i></div>\n<div class=\"captionnews\">Video nh gi chi tit Samsung Galaxy A12 c thc hin bi Th Gii Di ng.</div>\n<p>Kh bt ng vi mc gi r, nhng Samsung Galaxy A12 li s hu mn hnh git nc kch thc 6.5 inch trn vin m ra th gii rng ln, hin th c nhiu ni dung hn cho bn thoi mi tn hng khng gian gii tr.</p>\n<p>Cng tm nn PLS TFT LCD mang n kh nng ti to mu tt hn, cho cc ni dung bn xem u t c mu sc chn thc v sng ng nh tht.</p>\n<div class=\"imgwrap\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Galaxy A12\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Files/2022/01/12/1410374/galaxy-a12-15_1280x720-800-resize.jpg\" alt=\"Galaxy A12\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Files/2022/01/12/1410374/galaxy-a12-15_1280x720-800-resize.jpg\" /></div>\n<div class=\"captionnews\">Galaxy A12 s hu mt mn hnh vi kch thc kh to,   mnh gii tr v chi game mt cch thoi mi.</div>\n<p>ng lo s ht pin, v Galaxy A12 (2021) s p ng nhu cu s dng lu di ca bn nh c trang b vin pin dung lng 5.000 mAh. Thoi mi s dng smartphone c ngy m khng lo ht pin, khi ra ngoi cng khng cn em theo c sc hoc pin d phng na.</p>\n<div class=\"imgwrap\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Galaxy A12\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Files/2022/01/12/1410374/galaxy-a12-5_1280x720-800-resize.jpg\" alt=\"Galaxy A12\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Files/2022/01/12/1410374/galaxy-a12-5_1280x720-800-resize.jpg\" /></div>\n<div class=\"captionnews\">Galaxy A12 mang n cho mnh mt hiu nng n nh, mt m cng vi  l thi lng pin s dng hn 10 ting lin tc.</div>\n<p>Np y nng lng nhanh chng cho chic in thoi Galaxy A12 (2021) nh c tch hp cng ngh sc pin nhanh 15 W, bn khng cn phi ch i qu lu  c th s dng tip.</p>\n<p>Ph hp vi cc bn nh mun hc online hay xem nhng video hot hnh n ht ngy, trn mt chic mn hnh siu to khng l th cn g bng na ng khng no?</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a title=\"nh gi Galaxy A12 sau hn 1 nm s dng: Thit k p, pin 10 ting\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/tin-tuc/danh-gia-galaxy-a12-sau-hon-1-nam-ra-mat-1410374\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"nh gi Galaxy A12 sau hn 1