trong>l cng dn Vit Nam trn khp 63 tnh thnh. Ngi mua c quyn ng k ti khon hoc khng cn ng k  thc hin giao dch.</p>\n<p><strong>Thnh vin</strong>l bao gm c ngi mua v ngi tham kho thng tin, tho lun ti website.</p>\n<p>Ni dung bn Quy ch ny tun th theo cc quy nh hin hnh ca Vit Nam. Thnh vin khi tham gia website TMT Thegioididong.com phi t tm hiu trch nhim php l ca mnh i vi lut php hin hnh ca Vit Nam v cam kt thc hin ng nhng ni dung trong Quy ch ny.</p>\n<h2><strong>III. Quy trnh giao dch</strong></h2>\n<h3><u><strong>Dnh cho ngi mua hng ti website TMT Thegioididong.com</strong></u></h3>\n<p><strong>Bc 1:</strong>Tm sn phm cn mua.</p>\n<p><strong>Bc 2:</strong>Xem gi v thng tin chi tit sn phm , nu qu khch ng  mun t hng, qu khch n vo 1 trong 3 nt mua hng:</p>\n<p>+ t gi hng ti siu th.</p>\n<p>+ Mua tr gp.</p>\n<p>+ Mua ngay, giao hng tn ni.</p>\n<p><strong>Bc 3:</strong>Qu khch in y  thng tin theo mua hng theo mu:</p>\n<p>+ Nu qu khch c M gim gi, bn c th nhp trc tip vo form t mua  nhn vin giao hng c th phc v bn tt hn vi 1 mc gi chnh xc sau khi  gim.</p>\n<p>+ Qu khch hng ang s dng th ATM ni a hoc th tn dng Visa, Master qu khch c th thanh ton n hng bng cch lick vo Thanh ton trc tuyn (ATM, VISA, MASTER) v lm theo hng dn ca ngn hng.</p>\n<p>+ Nu qu khch ang s hu \"Phiu qu tng Thegioididong.com\", qu khch hng co lp bc trn th nhp \"M gim gi\" vo khung \"M gim gi\"  c tr tin trc tip vo n hng.</p>\n<p><strong>Bc 4:</strong>Sau khi nhn n hng ca ngi mua, Thegioididong.com s lin lc vi khch hng qua thng tin s in qu khch hng cung cp bng tng i 18001060 hoc 08.38102102  xc thc thng tin n hng.</p>\n<p><strong>Bc 5:</strong>Thegioididong.com giao hng tn nh n cho khch hng hoc khch hng n trc tip cc siu th Thegioididong.com trn ton quc  nhn hng.</p>\n<h3><u><strong>Dnh cho bn bn hng l Thegioididong.com</strong></u></h3>\n<p>+ Chun b sn xut ni dung gm: hnh nh sn phm chp thc t hoc hnh nh do hng sn xut cung cp, bi vit gii thiu, thng tin cu hnh sn phm.</p>\n<p>+ Nhp liu bng cng c qun l ring dnh ch