1 gi lm vic t khi tip nhn thng tin t ngi thc hin giao dch.</p>\n<h3><strong>VI. Bo v thng tin c nhn khch hng</strong></h3>\n<p>Thegioididong.com cam kt s bo mt nhng thng tin mang tnh ring t ca bn. Bn vui lng c bn Chnh sch bo mt di y  hiu hn nhng cam kt m chng ti thc hin, nhm tn trng v bo v quyn li ca ngi truy cp:</p>\n<p><strong>1. Mc ch v phm vi thu thp</strong></p>\n<p>-  truy cp v s dng mt s dch v ti Thegioididong.com, bn c th s c yu cu ng k vi chng ti thng tin c nhn (Email, H tn, S T lin lc). Mi thng tin khai bo phi m bo tnh chnh xc v hp php. Thegioididong.com khng chu mi trch nhim lin quan n php lut ca thng tin khai bo.</p>\n<p>- Chng ti cng c th thu thp thng tin v s ln ving thm, bao gm s trang bn xem, s links (lin kt) bn click v nhng thng tin khc lin quan n vic kt ni n site thegioididong.com. Chng ti cng thu thp cc thng tin m trnh duyt Web (Browser) bn s dng mi khi truy cp vo thegioididong.com, bao gm: a ch IP, loi Browser, ngn ng s dng, thi gian v nhng a ch m Browser truy xut n.</p>\n<p><strong>2. Phm vi s dng thng tin</strong></p>\n<p>Thegioididong.com thu thp v s dng thng tin c nhn bn vi mc ch ph hp v hon ton tun th ni dung ca Chnh sch bo mt ny.<br /><strong>C th:</strong><br />Khi cn thit, chng ti c th s dng nhng thng tin ny vo cc mc ch:</p>\n<p>- X l n hng: gi in/tin nhn xc nhn vic t hng, thng bo v trng thi n hng &amp; thi gian giao hng, xc nhn vic hu n hng (nu c).</p>\n<p>- Gi th ng/th cm n, gii thiu sn phm mi, dch v mi hoc cc chng trnh khuyn mi ca Thegioididong.com.</p>\n<p>- Gi thng tin v bo hnh sn phm.</p>\n<p>- Gii quyt khiu ni ca khch hng.</p>\n<p>- Thng tin trao thng (ca Thegioididong.com hoc ca hng).</p>\n<p>- Gi thng tin cho cng ty ti chnh  tip nhn, thm nh &amp; duyt h s tr gp.</p>\n<p>- Cc kho st  chm sc khch hng tt hn.</p>\n<p>- Xc nhn cc thng tin v k thut &amp; bo mt thng tin khch hng.</p>\n<p>- Cc trng hp c s yu cu ca c quan nh nc c thm quyn, theo ng quy nh ca php lut.</p>\n<strong>3. Thi gian lu tr thng tin</strong>\n<p>D liu c nhn ca Thnh v