(37, 'store_setup_survey_survey_q2_2022', 'survey', 'en_US', 'How is your store setup going?', 'Our goal is to make sure you have all the right tools to start setting up your store in the smoothest way possible.\r\nWed love to know if we hit our mark and how we can improve. To collect your thoughts, we made a 2-minute survey.', '{}', 'pending', 'woocommerce.com', '2022-05-15 09:44:38', NULL, 0, 'plain', '', 0, 0, 'info'),
